Apart from all printable games coloring pages, we also provide many activity coloring pages to print for free. These activity coloring pages contain different types of images to color, which may include printable coloring workbooks for kids, connect the dots activity coloring pages, printable masks to color, cut and paste activity coloring pages, printable cut-outs to color, etc.

This collection is especially meant for kids of small age. They like coloring pages of creatures and so this collection includes coloring pages like Coloring Pages of Animals, birds Coloring Pages, Butterfly Coloring Pages, etc.

Alligator is a predator belonging to Alligatoridae Family.  An average adult alligator weight's 350 kg and length is about 4 meter. A young Alligator being small eat fish, insects and worms where as a mature alligator eat large pray such as birds, deer and other reptiles. \r\nAlligators are territorial animals and are not friendly. So if you see an alligator, don't go near it.   Now its time to color a beautiful alligator coloring page. Adult alligators may be of olive, brown, gray, or black color, but their undersides are cream-colored. So lets start coloring...

Children love to color images of cartoon characters. For this reason, we bring coloring pages of famous cartoons like Disney Cartoons Coloring Pages including Mickey Mouse and Friends Coloring Pages, Aladdin and Jasmine Coloring Pages, Alice in the Wonderland Coloring Pages, etc. There is a huge variety of each of them.

We have a very huge gathering of Coloring Pages for Girls including All Disney Princess Coloring Pages, Coloring Pages of Barbie, Cinderella Coloring Pages, Snow White Coloring Pages, Little Mermaid Coloring Pages, etc.
Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs

We have a huge collection of holiday coloring pages. This section covers all major holidays like Easter Coloring Pages, Halloween Coloring Pages, Christmas Coloring Pages, Valentine Coloring Pages, Father’s Day Coloring Pages, Mother’s Day Coloring Pages, Thanks Giving Coloring Pages, and many more.

Preschool coloring pages are meant especially for teaching purpose where these coloring pages can be printed and used as teaching tools. For example, you can use ABC Coloring Pages, Coloring Pages of Fruits, Coloring Pages of Shapes, etc for coloring as well as for teaching kids about them.
